      "text": "Big Lots is the perfect stock for those who want to YOLO into a short term call short squeeze or a long term investment. Jan 2025 Calls are available to buy LEAPS for those looking for a long term option trade. I bought leaps & own the stock. $BIG offers a 6.5% dividend yield and has a PE ratio of 7. The underlying business is solid. They had a few missteps with excess inventory last quarter and fired their merchandising manager as a result. This cause a lot of write downs and a loss on the quarter. This was latched onto by the institutional shorts and here we are - a good company being shorted into the ground. Buy the calls! Buy the stock!"
